{"word":"G1991 - ἐπιστηρίζω - epistērízō - ep-ee-stay-rid'-zo - Confirm","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιστηρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epistērízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-stay-rid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Confirm</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திடப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to establish besides, strengthen more; to render more firm, confirm"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G4741 - στηρίζω - stērízō - stay-rid'-zo/4741\">G4741</a>; to <i>support further</i>, that is, <i>reestablish:</i> - confirm, strengthen.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1991/1991\">G1991</a>, <a href=\"#/G4740/4740\">G4740</a>, <a href=\"#/G4741/4741\">G4741</a>, <a href=\"#/G793/793\">G793</a>"}]}